<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />I waited patiently for Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">he listened to me and heard my cry.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />He brought me up out of a horrible pit, out of the miry clay,</para>

<para style="q1">and he set my feet on a rock and made my steps secure.</para>
